  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, whisk together soy sauce, brown sugar, garlic powder, and black pepper.",
    "Add the chicken pieces to the marinade and mix well.",
    "Cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 2 hours or overnight.",
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread the marinated chicken onto the skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Brush the yakitori glaze onto the chicken.",
    "Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, or until the chicken is cooked through and slightly charred.",
